25 August 2014 The Justice Crime and Prevention Cluster (JCPS) led by Minister of Defence and Military Veterans, Nosiviwe Mapisa -Nqakula (JCPS) will brief members of the media on the disruptions that unfolded in Parliament last week.Details of the briefing are as follows:Date: 26 August 2014 Time: 08h30 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape TownNB: There will be a video-link to GCIS Head Office, Tshedimosetso House 1035 Francis Baard Street, Hatfield, PTARSVP:Ireen Magwai Cell: 082 440 5676 ireen@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries:Nikelwa Tengimfene Cell: 082 574 5495Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)